comments: very nice teacher, helpful, cares about teaching. assignments are easy, and right out of the book. tests are easy. she gives you everything you need. easy class if you do the work, and she makes it interesting with discussions. best professor i\'ve ever had!

Definately do good on your quizes! She gives you all the infor for your tests. Very easy just take notes and study your quizes. Alittle too much personal discussions. Didnt care about other peoples pysch problems!
Very Easy Class. I would totally take it again!

Ugh. Where do I begin? The book is called "The Science of Psychology" but most of the time on this class is spent on introspective discussion. Writing assignments are disturbingly personal. (Ever hear of HIPAA?) Psychological issues and family problems are personal and no professor should force you to disclose them in order to get an A. Avoid!
loved her class. one of the only classes i wasnt bored to death. make sure to do the quizes and take notes. participation is big in her class.
Mrs. Magg gets an A as far as I\'m concerned!! shes always there to help. She checks her e-mail constantly Best professor ever!!!
Great Teacher along with a great personality. She is very helpful. I highly recommend her. You must study for this class in order to get a "A". If you get a bad grade, you didn\'t study.
